== Research
My research interests are transportation economics, transportation network modeling and optimization. In particular, I am working on
. Economical analysis of ride-sourcing market
. Shared mobility's impact on current transportation system
. Diverse AI applications in transportation system analysis
.. Machine Learningc for short-term traffic speed prediction
.. Deep Learning to forecast the passenger demand over an on-demand ride service
.. Reinforcement Learning to keep passenger-car matching process high efficiency

